{"about_the_game":"Introducing Idle Sphere, a stunningly beautiful incremental game that revolves around the captivating world of spheres.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nPrepare to be amazed as countless spheres come to life using cutting-edge technology. The game's graphics are seamlessly synchronized with the in-game currency, ensuring a mesmerizing visual experience. As you progress, you'll encounter increasingly complex, beautiful, and colossal spheres that will leave you in awe.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nIdle Sphere's gameplay is built on simple yet engaging upgrades, allowing you to enjoy the game intuitively. Immerse yourself in the satisfying experience of zooming in and out, admiring the exquisite beauty of the spheres.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nThe game features an extensive prestige system that adds depth to your journey. Although some upgrades may reset when you prestige, fear not! You'll emerge stronger and quickly regain your former power, ready to take on new challenges.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nDespite its simplicity, Idle Sphere offers a wealth of content for you to explore and enjoy. Dive into this captivating world of spheres and embark on an unforgettable incremental gaming adventure!","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Sphere Initiate","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3217600/ffdd1bdd9f9b95027ab96cfc3c2d4379fd75d2e2.jpg"},{"name":"Sphere Collector","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3217600/ffdd1bdd9f9b95027ab96cfc3c2d4379fd75d2e2.jpg"},{"name":"Sphere Hoarder","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3217600/ffdd1bdd9f9b95027ab96cfc3c2d4379fd75d2e2.jpg"},{"name":"Sphere Master","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3217600/ffdd1bdd9f9b95027ab96cfc3c2d4379fd75d2e2.jpg"},{"name":"Sphere Lord","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3217600/ffdd1bdd9f9b95027ab96cfc3c2d4379fd75d2e